Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Kagome and?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Inuyasha's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, so there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you haven't had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Kagome's been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demoness stole her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:38.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then, she wasn't thrown to\nthe ground and killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:51.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kaede! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:56.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human souls were being used to\nmove these puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bones have been baked into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She uses bones... That Urasue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bones and souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She stole my sister Kikyo's remains,\nand Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:28.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself.\NI'll recover Kikyo's bones for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't got much time, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We may well be\nmeeting up with Kikyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meeting Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:41.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Urasue uses her tricks to\nreincarnate Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she will become\na formidable foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have got to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a noisy chit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:08.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's in this water?\NIt smells like herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you've donned\nyour costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You look quite pretty dressed\nas a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your body is baked of\nhuman remains and graveyard soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I need do now is place\na human soul within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The herbs will soon cause your soul to\nleave your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:46.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will have you return it...\NKikyo's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo's soul... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean she's Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you fly more gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry. I thought time\nwas critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.\NGet me up there, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said Kagome's soul\nwould be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't be dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel awful... I can't... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:35.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The herbs should have caused\nher to lose consciousness by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you have a fragment\nof the Sacred Jewel!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What great fortune!\NI'll help myself to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the power\nof the Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This spirit is angered.\NKikyo's soul is mad with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel sick... I'm going to throw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is a powerful grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:09.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something damnable must surely have\nhappened to her in her previous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't call my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! It's leaving her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The second you said her name,\nher heart skipped a beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Kikyo's soul sprang forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's soul has\nentered Kikyo's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Wake up, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl is just an empty shell now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll pickle her later\nfor my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, Urasue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dared to use\nmy sister Kikyo's bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:03.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have used my powers to turn\NKikyo's remains into flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You could say\NI am her birth mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo will do anything\NI ask of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:15.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, use your powers to rid us\nof these bothersome... Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you alive?\NI know I sealed you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heh! Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:47.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It took me about 50 years to get out,\nbut I'm fine, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:55.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you turn\nagainst me, Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that? That blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:18.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that the fatal wound\nyou inflicted on Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying I killed Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! That's how my sister died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede... I don't remember\ndoing any such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Truly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:46.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say you did not inflict\nthe wound that killed Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh-What... What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never expected to\nhear such excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's unbecoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it... Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you remember saying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That you'd become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human? Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said you'd become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:23.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believed you, and took\nthe Sacred Jewel to you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have absolutely no wish\nto become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sure appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It needs to absorb more bitterness\nand ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those villagers... I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could he have done such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying I betrayed you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I gathered the\nlast of my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and bound you to the\ntree with my arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were never to meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop this, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am your sister Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have lived 50 years since your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:13.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you protect Inuyasha, Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mustn't, Kikyo.\NInuyasha is not the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you been taken in\nby this half-demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you and I\nshare the same blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you refuse to follow\nyour older sister's command?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You told me that you\nwanted to become human...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Become human and live with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will happen to Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So long as Kikyo holds\non to her hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,her soul will not grow still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So long as her soul\ndoes not return to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome will continue to slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I truly loved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence! I was a fool for wishing,\neven for a second, to live with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I died hating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My spirit cannot shed that hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So long as you live,\NI cannot be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:37.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want you to destroy my sister's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:44.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her rebirth is just a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must release her soul\nfrom within.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no use!\NSo long as the hatred is not erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this soul will not return to her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! All it takes is your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo's arrow has\novercome the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:34.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kagome.\NShe's trying to take back her soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:39.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I... I... I still!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kikyo... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo! So, she still has some spirit left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:15.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All that's keeping Kikyo going\nnow is her deeply held grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems most of her soul\nhas returned to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like her pent-up grudges have\nbeen absorbed well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,into the bones and graveyard earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The once pure maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is now a demon filled with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that lovely? Heh-heh-heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I remain near that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she'll take the rest of my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got to get away... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:04.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't go on like this.\NYou must return to Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:17.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I return to that girl,\nthat means I will no longer be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I die, you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I die, you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo used her spiritual powers to\nprotect the Sacred Jewel from demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I needed the Sacred Jewel, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:46.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to become\na full-fledged demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:07.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!\NWhy do you never finish me off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit bothering me.\NI don't want to waste my arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could just get my hands\non that Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no intention of killing Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo would never kill me, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I know you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've never talked\nlike this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... How do I look?\NDo I look human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:01.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never show anyone my weakness.\NI must never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, some demon\nwill get the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:09.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm human, but I mustn't be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and I have things in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:16.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, the half-demon.\NThat's why I couldn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:21.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! Complaining?\NIt's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess... it's unlike me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking at Kikyo's sad face...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the first time in my life,\NI felt like I'd done something wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that day,\nall I could think about was Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was always near{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was always with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me... A human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure you can.\NYou're half human, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the Sacred Jewel fell into\nthe hands of a true demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,its powers would greatly increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if it was used to\nturn you into a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Jewel would be purified and\nwould probably cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what would\nhappen to you, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My duty is to protect the Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without the Jewel,\NI'd become an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no second thoughts...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believed I could live\nas a human with Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted that life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... It was I who\nwas betrayed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I let down my guard,\nshe tried to kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I managed to dodge her arrows...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then attacked the village\nto steal the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, she nailed me to that tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:36.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you betray me, Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:44.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...! Why did we come to this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:21:59.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems that Kikyo\ndied hating Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a bit depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but our search for the\NSacred Jewel still continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons come after\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, he isn't a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, he has unbelievable\npower in his sealed right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:07.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A good guy? Bad guy?\NOr is he nothing but a lecher?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.64,0:24:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Mystical Hand of the\NAmorous Monk, Miroku"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
